IMAPStore nju-remote
Host imap.exmail.qq.com
Port 993
User daiwz@nju.edu.cn
PassCmd "pass show muw/daiwz@nju.edu.cn"
AuthMechs LOGIN
# SSLType IMAPS
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore nju-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/nju/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/nju/INBOX
Flatten _

Channel nju
Expunge Both
Far  :nju-remote:
Near :nju-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile
